<h1 id="toc13"><span>PSYCHE Records</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc14"><span>History of the Roc Project (cont.)</span></h2>
<p>J-CAED-02 succeeded in neutralizing the threat and was sent for Airbase Barcid Echo for a final checkup. After minor repairs, the drone was then transported to Airbase Gaulle Alfa for preparation for transport to Airbase Renegade Alfa for christening&#8230;</p>
